sequenceDiagram
  box rgba(229, 241, 255, 0.8) Edge
    actor User
    participant SPA
  end
  box rgba(236, 245, 233, 0.8) Platform
    participant API
    participant Queue
    participant Worker
  end

  User->>+SPA: Upload CSV
  SPA->>+API: POST /imports
  API->>API: Parse metadata
  API-)Queue: Enqueue import job
  Queue-->>-API: Ack
  API-->>-SPA: 202 Accepted
  SPA-->>User: Show import tracking id

  Note over Queue,Worker: Async processing continues off the request path

  Queue->>+Worker: Deliver import job
  Worker->>Worker: Normalize rows
  Worker-->>-Queue: Complete
